specs/t-010@20260408t223256zb-spec.md:11:2. **Heartbeat payload** — Call `ollama_health()` inside `format_half_hour_heartbeat()` and add an `"ollama"` key to the returned payload dict. Also append a one-line Ollama summary to the heartbeat text.
specs/t-010@20260408t223256zb-spec.md:13:3. **`CypherClawArt.status_display()`** — Extend with an optional `ollama: dict | None = None` parameter. When provided, render a compact Ollama section after the pet section showing per-socket status, model names, and latency.
specs/t-010@20260408t223256zb-spec.md:15:4. **Integration test** — Test that `/status` output includes Ollama health text when `ollama_health()` returns healthy/unhealthy instances, and that the heartbeat payload contains the `"ollama"` key.
